@startuml
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam stateFontSize 12

[*] --> Unauthenticated

state Unauthenticated : No valid JWT.\nAccess limited to\n[AllowAnonymous] endpoints.

state Authenticated : Valid JWT present.\nUser identity and claims\nestablished.

state Authorized : Privilege claim matches\nrequired operation + aggregate.\nRequest proceeds.

state Forbidden : Privilege check failed.\nResponse contains\n"Unauthorized" error.

Unauthenticated --> Authenticated : Valid credentials submitted\nJWT issued via /api/user/token
Unauthenticated --> Unauthenticated : Invalid credentials\n(exception thrown)

Authenticated --> Authorized : Privilege check passes\n(claim found for operation + aggregate)
Authenticated --> Forbidden : Privilege check fails\n(no matching claim)
Authenticated --> Unauthenticated : Token expires\n(JWT lifetime exceeded)

Authorized --> Authenticated : Next request\n(token still valid)
Forbidden --> Authenticated : Next request\n(different endpoint)

@enduml
